'''四旋翼飞行器'''（quadrotor aircraft），又稱'''四轴直升机'''（quadcopter）或'''四轉子'''（quad），是用四个[[旋翼|旋翼]]产生[[升力|升力]]的[[多轴飞行器|多轴飞行器]]，是[[直升机|直升机]]的一种。和[[固定翼飞机|固定翼飞机]]不同，它通过旋翼提供的推力使飞机[[垂直起降|垂直起降]]、[[悬停|悬停]]、进行各种飞行。它的四个旋翼大小相同，分布位置接近对称，其中两个旋翼与另两个转动方向相反。对于简单的设计来说，仅仅通过调整不同旋翼之间的相对速度来调节不同位置的推力，并克服每个旋翼之间的[[扭矩|反扭力矩]]，就可以控制飞机维持姿态、或完成平飞、转向、翻滚、倒飞和侧飞等各种机动飞行。这一点和常见的只有一个主旋翼的单旋翼[[直升机|直升机]]不同，单旋翼直升机的尾桨只起到抵消主旋翼产生的反扭矩，控制飞机偏航运动的功能。

早期飞机设计中，四轴飞行器被用来解决[[旋翼航空器|-{zh-tw:旋翼航空器;zh-cn:旋翼机;}-]]的[[力矩|扭矩]]问题。主副[[旋翼|旋翼]]的设计也可以解决扭矩问题，但副旋翼不能提供升力，效率低。且使用尾桨的设计在结构上比使用多旋翼要复杂很多。因此四轴飞行器是最早的一批比空气重的垂直起降飞行器。<ref>{{cite book | last = Leishman | first = J.G. | title = Principles of Helicopter Aerodynamics | publisher = Cambridge University Press | year = 2000 | location = New York, NY}}</ref>但是早期的型号性能很差，难于操控和大型化。<ref name="anderson81">{{Cite journal | last = Anderson | first = S.B. | title = Historical Overview of V/STOL Aircraft Technology | journal = NASA Technical Memorandum 81280 | date = March | year = 1981 | url = http://ntrs.nasa.gov/archive/nasa/casi.ntrs.nasa.gov/19810010574_1981010574.pdf | postscript = <!--None--> | access-date = 2013-05-16 | archive-date = 2011-06-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110605193810/http://ntrs.nasa.gov/archive/nasa/casi.ntrs.nasa.gov/19810010574_1981010574.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>尤其是油门的控制难以做到精确和迅速。更加上传统的直升机构型在巡航时的效率要优于四轴飞行器。故此在直升机的技术问题得以解决后，四轴飞行器迅速从飞行器设计方式中销声匿迹了。

[[File:Flight_Quadrotor.JPG|left]]
近来四轴飞行器在[[无人机|无人机]]领域获得了新生。隨著智慧型手機的發展，帶動電子[[陀螺儀|陀螺儀]]、[[GPS|GPS]]、[[飞行控制系统|电传飞行控制系统]]的發展，並以及油门响应速度迅速的电动机作为动力系统，克服了四轴飞行器的主要缺点。四轴飞行器飞行稳定，操控灵活，可以在户内和户外使用。<ref name="dasc04">{{cite conference | first = G.M. | last = Hoffmann | coauthors = Rajnarayan, D.G., Waslander, S.L., Dostal, D., Jang, J.S., and Tomlin, C.J. | title = The Stanford Testbed of Autonomous Rotorcraft for Multi Agent Control (STARMAC) | booktitle = In the Proceedings of the 23rd Digital Avionics System Conference | pages = 12.E.4/1–10 | date = November 2004 | location = Salt Lake City, UT | url = http://hoffmann.stanford.edu/papers/Hoffmann_et_al_Quadrotor_DASC04.pdf | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070626203154/http://hoffmann.stanford.edu/papers/Hoffmann_et_al_Quadrotor_DASC04.pdf | archivedate = 2007-06-26 | access-date = 2013-05-16 }}</ref><ref name="büchi11">{{cite book| last = Büchi | first = Roland | title = Fascination Quadrocopter | year = 2011 | location = ISBN 978-3-8423-6731-9}}</ref>和直升机相比，它有许多优点：它的旋翼角度固定，结构简单。<ref name="acra2006">{{cite conference | first = P. | last = Pounds | coauthors = Mahony, R., Corke, P. | title = Modelling and Control of a Quad-Rotor Robot | booktitle = In the Proceedings of the Australasian Conference on Robotics and Automation | date = December 2006 | location = Auckland, New Zealand | url = http://www.araa.asn.au/acra/acra2006/papers/paper_5_26.pdf | access-date = 2013-05-16 | archive-date = 2013-05-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130512142906/http://www.araa.asn.au/acra/acra2006/papers/paper_5_26.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>每个旋翼的叶片比较短，叶片末端的[[线速度|线速度]]慢，发生碰撞时冲击力小，不容易损坏，对人也更安全。有些小型四轴飞行器的旋翼有外框，避免碰撞。<ref name="hoffmanAugust2007">{{cite conference | first = G. | last = Hoffman | coauthors = Huang, H., Waslander, S.L., Tomlin, C.J. | title = Quadrotor Helicopter Flight Dynamics and Control: Theory and Experiment | booktitle = In the Conference of the American Institute of Aeronautics and Astronautics | date = 20–23 August 2007 | location = Hilton Head, South Carolina | url = http://hoffmann.stanford.edu/papers/Quadrotor_Dynamics_GNC07.pdf | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100813162324/http://hoffmann.stanford.edu/papers/Quadrotor_Dynamics_GNC07.pdf | archivedate = 2010年8月13日 | access-date = 2013年5月16日 }}</ref>

因为四轴飞行器體積小、重量輕，攜帶方便，能輕易進入人不易進入的各種惡劣環境。常用来制作模型，也用来執行[[航拍|航拍]]電影取景、實時監控、地形勘探等飛行任務。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blog.makezine.com/archive/2010/01/how-to-quadrocopter-based-on-arduin.html |title=Arduino-based quadcopter |access-date=2013-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111211005108/http://blog.makezine.com/archive/2010/01/how-to-quadrocopter-based-on-arduin.html |archive-date=2011-12-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ng.uavp.ch/moin/FrontPage |title=UAVP-NG based quadcopter |accessdate=2013-05-16 |archive-date=2013-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515111259/http://ng.uavp.ch/moin/FrontPage |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2009年電影《[[三傻大闹宝莱坞|三傻大闹宝莱坞]]》中，就有描述當時剛開始萌芽的多軸飛行器，其中男主角從垃圾桶撿回後來拍到學生慘劇的那部，便是四轴飞行器的一種。
